==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Shortening
<hw>Short"en*ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of making
or becoming short or shorter.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Cookery)</fld> <def>That which renders pastry short
or friable, as butter, lard, etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Shorthand</ent>⟦br⟧
